name: vit-pytorch
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "vit-pytorch" %}
{% set version = "0.25.5" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: a41bebbcada080d56a19dd0ffd69c9efd4379aabc7af19e7d71f9c30e6cdead3

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - pytest-runner
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - einops >=0.3
    - pytorch >=1.6
    - torchvision

test:
  imports:
    - vit_pytorch
  source_files:
    - tests/test.py
  requires:
    - pytest
  commands:
    - pytest tests/*.py

about:
  home: "https://github.com/lucidrains/vit-pytorch"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Vision Transformer (ViT) - Pytorch"
  dev_url: https://github.com/lucidrains/vit-pytorch

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lucidrains
